{"type": "article", "id": 24602, "title": "蘑菇形的极简灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-29T06:59:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154813RolBcr4tjLf0bQu3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组灯来自伦敦设计工作室 Industrial Facility ，它有一个像蘑菇一样的圆盘形灯罩，灯罩下面是极细的长灯柱，两者间构成了对比和反差，也让这盏灯体现出了极简和轻盈的美感。设计师认为这就是街上常见的灯，它包括落地灯、台灯和与桌子相连的灯。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154811aoh8jFRZ3f7dDULQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154811KUAIuSq5lvLbZ1BC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154812NtWkg32pf0UA8eax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061548120X9xgKyJDQk3Wu5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154813Czrf4MvPp5UV7eEs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}